// Hargo, 25/05/2026: when a damage-fee DD has been attempted <1 working day
// ago, the recheck must wait until the NEXT WORKING DAY — NOT the next
// hourly run. We dedup per (agreementId, working-day-ISO): once an agreement
// has been reported as pending on a given working day, subsequent hourly
