// Run approval monitor once on startup (catch anything missed during downtime).
// Wait until BOT_USER_ID is resolved before firing — running before auth.test
// resolves causes the dedup-by-bot-user gate to misfire and the "Marking as
// complete" message to re-post on every redeploy. 20/05/2026 spam incident.
